{"tid":2037590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中資銀行要求員工聯署支持國安法","createTime":"2020-05-27T05:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T10:10:40.000Z","uid":340796,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf666752be6c43c5d5bb92af2191b1dcd513d43","tid":2037590,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"HONG KONG -- Chinese banks and brokerages are asking Hong Kong staff to sign a petition supporting national security legislation set to pass the National People's Congress on Thursday, the Nikkei Asian Review has learned.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I had an unexpected task this morning,&quot; said one analyst at a Chinese investment bank, who gave her name as Mandy. &quot;My boss asked everyone in the team to sign this paper.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Printed in blue, the color of the city's pro-Beijing camp, the petition asked signatories to support the national security legislation as well as &quot;anti-Hong Kong independence; anti-sedition; anti-terrorism; anti-foreign interference.&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The same form has also been circulated in street booths set up by pro-Beijing political parties over the last few days.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Even though management said the petition is &quot;voluntary,&quot; Mandy, the employee, said the bank's human resources officer was checking which employees had signed.</span><br />\n<strong>人力資源部會check 未有簽名的員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIn addition to the hardcopy, staff at Guotai Junan Securities were asked to put their names to an online petition that required participants to a<span style=\"color: red;\">dd the last four digits of their ID card number</span>, according to four people who at the brokerage.<br />\n<strong>要填身份證號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n已知有四間：交行, ICBC, 海通, 國泰君安<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Hong-Kong-protests/China-banks-demand-employees-sign-pro-security-law-petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FSpotlight%2FHong-Kong-protests%2FChina-banks-demand-employees-sign-pro-security-law-petition&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=5db49ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Hong-Kong-protests/China-banks-demand-employees-sign-pro-security-law-petition</a>"},{"pid":"88aa3f5e2555acc8cc310515c870d8d8ae2e2904","tid":2037590,"uid":260694,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"辭職啦仲做，反中資死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8567d662d24c3327f175e0d843c57704a932fed4","tid":2037590,"uid":340796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88aa3f5e2555acc8cc310515c870d8d8ae2e2904","tid":2037590,"uid":260694,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"辭職啦仲做，反中資死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"俾番骨氣<br />\n唔好簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d8c9cb48a0bd48507426da3fa716178ce2ee2c","tid":2037590,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"揚咗出嚟即係聯署已經無用"},{"pid":"00918ce486e62c5a8e5461dee3740b15c6608b31","tid":2037590,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"仲做中資？有仔都唔認你啦！"},{"pid":"e9c4ed4cdaaa0f11c40461d1c91b13116e13111e","tid":2037590,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d8c9cb48a0bd48507426da3fa716178ce2ee2c","tid":2037590,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:56:51.000Z",